   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00002-000-00137"/>Herrn D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb168940" type="place">XVIII Spöttelgasse 7</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline><seg rend="left"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00002-000-00138"/><date>Montag</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><time>mittg</time>, <rs ref="#pmb189" type="place">Se<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>ering</rs></seg><seg rend="right">»<rs ref="#pmb634" type="place">Ehg. Johann</rs>«</seg></dateline></opener><p><salute>lieber,</salute> ich bin wegen dem ewigen Kopfweh und anderem für 5–6 Tage
               hier herauf gegangen. Habe mein Rad mit. Sehen wir uns noch vor Ihrer Abrei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e?</p><closer><signed>Hugo</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
